    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/7d83fd6480c2ad275f1459bb3f5f075f.poster.avif?t=1766421047\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/7d83fd6480c2ad275f1459bb3f5f075f.webm?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/7d83fd6480c2ad275f1459bb3f5f075f.mp4?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lubs: True Alliance is a Middle Age fantasy game, which presents you different experience with its  dynamic and continuous fighting scenes of Hack &amp; Slash style as well as rich story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/da524ccb3dc63edcc63ed8d49d386217.poster.avif?t=1766421047\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/da524ccb3dc63edcc63ed8d49d386217.webm?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/da524ccb3dc63edcc63ed8d49d386217.mp4?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tilennar Kingdom, which is surrounded by intrigues and betrayals and verge of collapsing looks for a way out with its holy judges. The purpose of Reindall who is chosen by the holy judges is to make his kingdom in peace by exposing the rebels' (Kriltons) secret plans. He shall understand the truths and lies and also who is enemy or ally in this journey. Make Reindall's sword sharp and his mind sharper! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/f03a87828169a9265c0adfe7b3db9507.poster.avif?t=1766421047\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/f03a87828169a9265c0adfe7b3db9507.webm?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131880/extras/f03a87828169a9265c0adfe7b3db9507.mp4?t=1766421047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
